data.description: Elegant Residence with Five Bedrooms and Three-and-a-Half Bathrooms. Discover this grand three-sided brick home boasting five bedrooms and three-and-a-half bathrooms. As you step inside, you'll find a formal dining room and a living room, ideal for hosting guests or enjoying intimate gatherings. The cozy family room is adorned with a charming fireplace, providing the perfect setting for relaxation. Adjacent to this, an inviting eat-in kitchen awaits, featuring stained cabinets, a convenient breakfast bar, and a sunlit bayed breakfast area, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee. Your master retreat is truly exceptional, with an oversized layout, a sitting room, a tray ceiling, and a private bathroom that promises tranquility. Additionally, you'll discover spacious secondary bedrooms that offer comfort and convenience. Outside, a vast backyard beckons, complete with a welcoming patio, offering an abundance of space for outdoor activities, be it for children to run and play or for hosting outdoor gatherings.
